  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Realtime-Elastography scores I-IV in thyroid nodules</measure>
    <description>Scores: I-II: benign; III-IV: malignant nodules. The sensitivity and specificity of Realtime-Elastography for the diagnosis of malignant thyroid nodules will be calculated on the basis of above-specified criteria. Cytology is used as reference method for benign nodules and histology for malignant nodules.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
